<br>
Your DPS does not come solely from your damage bonus, IMO the massive inherint beleif in &quot;dmg bonus &gt; all&quot; has totally perverted the ability of someone to desire a weapon with a delay over 20...It's utter crap. Ratio still owns hardcore, and a 26/28 can sure as hell own some serious mucho grandes ass in the taunt and damage department. Not to mention, whilst still avoiding a higher percentage of riposts from mobs with a faster weapon.<br>
<br>
As it stands, a 26/28 is a darnsight better mainhand than a lot of other options. Aswell as not being as situational as an EB mainhand when your intent is to keep a steady amount of aggro, but not take it from someone else unintentionally.<br>
<br>
The proc is just a booby prize, its still a bloody nice weapon that prolly dishes out more dps than most common mainhand's.<br>
<br>
Grats, hope you have fun with it.<br>
<br>
~Faate <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=grobsmash>Grobsmash</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 313<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/11/03 7:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3127.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://cot.emich.edu/personal/screenshots/Gawdz/candleandflag.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: lknl/km</span><hr size=1> read my post again and decided not enough sleep + to much allergy medicine = a post of babbling<br>
